==English==
===Noun===
'''myopia'''

# {{pathology}} A disorder of the [[vision]] where distant objects appear blurred because the eye focuses their images in front of the [[retina]] instead of on it. Also called [[shortsightedness]], [[nearsightedness]].
# A lack of imagination, discernment or long-range perspective in thinking or planning.

